        {
          "_name": "article21",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article021\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButton\" title=\"Buttons\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#d8c3a5\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#fafafa\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                        <b>Game rules</b></h5>\n                    <h6 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .main-button\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">(Source: Wikipedia)</h6>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-3  main-button\" mbr-if=\"showButton\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                        <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Learn more\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-lg-8 side-features\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li>Each player starts from the center of their perimeter line, and the objective is to move their pawn to the opposite perimeter line. The first player to achieve this goal wins.</li>\n                            <li>On their turn, a player can choose to move their pawn horizontally or vertically, or place a wall. A wall cannot be jumped over and must be moved around.</li>\n                            <li>If two pawns are face to face, the player whose turn it is can jump over the opponent and land behind them. It is not possible to “block” a player completely using walls; they must always be left with a possible path to reach the goal.</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            "& when (@reverseContent)": {
              ".row": {
                "flex-direction": "row-reverse"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".item-wrapper": {
              "background": "@cardbg",
              "padding": "2.25rem 2.25rem 1rem 2.25rem",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "padding": "2rem 1.5rem 0.5rem 1.5rem"
              },
              "@media (min-width: 992px) and (max-width: 1200px)": {
                "padding": "2rem 1.5rem 0.5rem 1.5rem"
              }
            },
            ".main-button": {
              "margin-bottom": "2rem",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "2rem"
              }
            },
            ".counter-container": {
              "ul": {
                "margin": "0",
                "padding-left": "2.25rem",
                "list-style": "none",
                "li": {
                  "position": "relative",
                  "list-style": "none",
                  "margin-bottom": "2rem",
                  "&:before": {
                    "position": "absolute",
                    "left": "-1.5em",
                    "content": "\"\"",
                    "display": "flex",
                    "justify-content": "center",
                    "align-items": "center",
                    "color": "@iconColor",
                    "background-color": "@iconColor",
                    "width": "0.5em",
                    "height": "0.5em",
                    "top": "0.4em",
                    "border-radius": "50%"
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text UL": {
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle, .main-button": {
              "color": "#000000"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "vhBE98pBDq",
